{"title":"Conversation","author":{"name":"Ai"},"publishDate":"2011-08-15","lines":[{"line":"We smile at each other","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"and I lean back against the wicker couch.","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"How does it feel to be dead? I say.","stanza":1,"number":3},{"line":"You touch my knees with your blue fingers.","stanza":1,"number":4},{"line":"And when you open your mouth,","stanza":1,"number":5},{"line":"a ball of yellow light falls to the floor","stanza":1,"number":6},{"line":"and burns a hole through it.","stanza":1,"number":7},{"line":"Don’t tell me, I say. I don’t want to hear.","stanza":1,"number":8},{"line":"Did you ever, you start,","stanza":1,"number":9},{"line":"wear a certain kind of dress","stanza":1,"number":10},{"line":"and just by accident,","stanza":1,"number":11},{"line":"so inconsequential you barely notice it,","stanza":1,"number":12},{"line":"your fingers graze that dress","stanza":1,"number":13},{"line":"and you hear the sound of a knife cutting paper,","stanza":1,"number":14},{"line":"you see it too","stanza":1,"number":15},{"line":"and you realize how that image","stanza":1,"number":16},{"line":"is simply the extension of another image,","stanza":1,"number":17},{"line":"that your own life","stanza":1,"number":18},{"line":"is a chain of words","stanza":1,"number":19},{"line":"that one day will snap.","stanza":1,"number":20},{"line":"Words, you say, young girls in a circle, holding hands,","stanza":1,"number":21},{"line":"and beginning to rise heavenward","stanza":1,"number":22},{"line":"in their confirmation dresses,","stanza":1,"number":23},{"line":"like white helium balloons,","stanza":1,"number":24},{"line":"the wreathes of flowers on their heads spinning,","stanza":1,"number":25},{"line":"and above all that,","stanza":1,"number":26},{"line":"that’s where I’m floating,","stanza":1,"number":27},{"line":"and that’s what it’s like","stanza":1,"number":28},{"line":"only ten times clearer,","stanza":1,"number":29},{"line":"ten times more horrible.","stanza":1,"number":30},{"line":"Could anyone alive survive it?","stanza":1,"number":31}]}